---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy | NomadBurn";
const description =
  "NomadBurn privacy policy covering calculator inputs, optional AI diagnosis, logs, cookies, analytics, and contact requests.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonicalPath="/privacy-policy/">
  <section class="content-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy policy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Last updated July 8, 2026. NomadBurn is designed to work without an account, payment flow, or
      required signup.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-panel">
    <h2>Information you provide</h2>
    <p>
      The calculator asks for planning inputs such as savings, income, destination, accommodation
      style, tax reserve, payment loss, and fixed costs. The basic calculator runs in your browser
      and does not require you to create an account.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you contact NomadBurn by email, we receive the information you choose to send, such as your
      email address, message, page URL, cost correction, or support request.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-panel">
    <h2>Optional AI diagnosis</h2>
    <p>
      If you choose to run the optional AI diagnosis, the calculator payload and result are sent to a
      Cloudflare Pages Function so the diagnosis can be generated. When an AI provider key is
      configured, that function may send the payload to Google Gemini to produce the response. If the
      provider is unavailable, NomadBurn falls back to a local non-AI diagnosis.
    </p>
    <p>
      Do not enter sensitive personal data into the calculator. Use rounded planning numbers instead
      of exact account balances or private financial details.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-panel">
    <h2>Logs, cookies, and analytics</h2>
    <p>
      NomadBurn is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may process standard request information
      such as IP address, user agent, URLs requested, timestamps, and security signals to operate and
      protect the site.
    </p>
    <p>
      NomadBurn does not currently require login cookies, advertising cookies, or payment cookies.
      If analytics, email capture, or paid products are added later, this policy should be updated
      before those features are used.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-panel">
    <h2>How information is used</h2>
    <ul class="plain-list">
      <li>To operate the calculator and optional AI diagnosis.</li>
      <li>To respond to emails, corrections, privacy requests, and support messages.</li>
      <li>To improve city assumptions, page quality, accessibility, and site reliability.</li>
      <li>To protect the site from abuse, spam, or technical attacks.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="content-panel">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions or deletion requests related to messages you sent, email
      <a href="mailto:hello@nomadburn.com">hello@nomadburn.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
